	<section id="containers">
		<h2>Containers</h2>

		<ul>
			<li>Most content should be wrapped in a <code>.container</code> div</li>
			<li>Only hero banners etc should be full width, for impact</li>
			<li>Containers have a max width and centrally aligned horizontally</li>
			<li>Can extend it in SASS via the <code>%container</code> placeholder</li>
			<li>Not designed to be nested</li>
		</ul>

		{% example "html" -%}
			<div class="container">
				<p>Some content e.g. a grid goes here</p>
			</div>
		{%- endexample %}

	</section>

